    About Hotel St Paul's

    Housed in what was once a nineteenth-century school, St Paul’s Hotel offers boutique accommodations and fine dining in the Hammersmith region of London. Luxury guestrooms feature stylish décor and en suite bathroom with complimentary toiletries. In-room amenities include TV, minibar, safe, tea and coffee-making facilities, and air conditioning. Bathrobes and ironing facilities are available on request, while the hotel also offers meeting and event facilities. The Melody Restaurant, located on-site, offers European cuisine with a modern twist. Guests can tuck into a continental or cooked breakfast each morning, while the hotel lounge bar is ideal for sitting back and relaxing. St Paul’s Hotel is located between the Olympia exhibition centre and Hammersmith Apollo theatre, both of which are less than ten minutes away on foot. Kensington Palace, Stamford Bridge football stadium, and the Royal Albert Hall are all within two miles of the hotel, and all served by the nearby Hammersmith underground station.

    About Thistle Bloomsbury Park

    Wedged between central London and the West End, Thistle Bloomsbury Park (otherwise known as Bloomsbury Park Hotel) is a 3-star establishment in a renovated Edwardian building. West End theatres are in easy reach for guests, by foot or with the Russell Square metro several hundred metres away. All rooms come with safe, flat-screen Smart TV with Freeview channels, Bluetooth speakers,free Wi-Fi and complimentary tea, coffee and toiletries. Public parking can be found nearby, room-service is offered 24 hours a day and laundry and dry-cleaning services are available. Thistle Bloomsbury Park offers high-quality conference and event facilities, including LCD projectors and screens. The richly-furnished house brasserie serves breakfast and dinner in style, the Bloomsbury Bar has drinks and snacks midday to midnight and there is a cellar bar for functions. Soho London, British Museum, Covent Garden and the West End are all easily walkable in less than ten minutes. This accommodation is also known as Bloomsbury Park Hotel, Hotel Bloomsbury Park, Bloomsbury Park - A Thistle Associate Hotel London, and England.

    Hilton London Kensington is situated in the leafy district of Holland Park, just 30 minutes from Heathrow Airport and with excellent transport links into central London. Enjoy the relaxed atmosphere of this contemporary Kensington hotel amid the fresh, bright decor of a guest room with WiFi access, a mini-bar and LCD flat-screen TV. Choose a deluxe room for extra amenities or a suite for a separate living room. Executive rooms offer Executive Lounge access with free continental breakfast, afternoon tea and snacks, and open bar. This stylish hotel in Kensington also provides family-friendly accommodation, adjoining rooms, and accessible and day use rooms. Car parking and a 24-hour Concierge desk is available. Hold a business or social event at Hilton London Kensington, with 11 function rooms for 12-370, including five dedicated Hilton meeting rooms. Attend to business in our ground floor Executive Lounge and business centre with WiFi, video conferencing services and assistance from the helpful reception staff. Savour a delicious buffet breakfast in the chic WestEleven Restaurant. Modern art adorns the walls of this chic London Kensington restaurant, tastefully decorated in mahogany and purple tones. Hilton London Kensington's flagship brasserie also serves a delicious breakfast buffet. Meet with friends in the Avenue Bar & Lounge, or enjoy a freshly brewed coffee while surfing the web. Keep fit in our LivingWell gym and relax in the sauna and steam room.

    About Ten Manchester Street Hotel

    A ten minute stroll from London's bustling Oxford Street, Ten Manchester Street is an elegant four star boutique hotel in Marylebone.  Set back from the lively city atmosphere just a bit for optimal tranquility, this locale is the perfect vacation luxury.   Rooms vary in size and amenity at Ten Manchester Street, offering mini bars, exquisite toiletries, espresso machines, bathrobes/slippers and DVD players upon request. Hotel features comprise complimentary Wi-Fi, Afternoon Tea, and such unique venues as the exclusive Cigars at No.Ten, an indoor cigar terrace and shop. Dine in at the stunning full menu Dieci Restaurant for the finest Italian cuisine and rare wines. Don't miss nearby attractions of Regents Park, The Victoria and Albert Museum, Soho, The Sherlock Holmes Museum and West End Theatre Land, most within walking distance or a short ride.
